      "rationale": "The CFD solver (ANSYS Fluent 2023 R1) is a commercially licensed code with documented V&V history and ISO 9001-certified development process. Internal SQA records confirm version control, regression testing, and release notes were reviewed prior to simulation execution. Achieved Gradation 2 exceeds the Gradation 1 requirement for MRL 2.",
