      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "rationale": "Manufactured solution tests for the incompressible Navier-Stokes solver confirmed second-order spatial convergence. Taylor-Green vortex benchmark reproduced to within 0.3% of the analytic solution. Order-of-accuracy testing documented in the solver's published verification report (ANSYS, 2022). Gradation 2 achieved against Gradation 1 requirement.",
